# Cursor Rules — ai-automation-hustle

> **Read this first.** Then if you need more, see `CLAUDE.md`, `SYSTEM_BLUEPRINT_PHASE1.md`, and `docs/CLIENT_DEPLOYMENT.md`.

---

## 1. What this project is

**Repo name:** `ai-automation-hustle` (GitHub: `charan11102543-ai/RoM-Jaran`)
**Owner:** Solo operator in Thailand (Charan)
**Business model:** **Agency** — Setup 15,000 THB + Retainer 6,000–15,000 THB/month
**Target niche:** Thai dental clinics in Bangkok (1–3 branches)
**Product:** AI-powered LINE OA + web lead capture / qualification / booking for clinics
**Tech:** Next.js 16 (App Router, Turbopack), Prisma 7 + PostgreSQL, NextAuth (credentials), OpenAI, pnpm

This is **NOT a SaaS** to sell self-serve. Each client gets their own deployed instance. The codebase is the agency's **delivery asset**, not the product itself.

