## 5. Common commands

```bash
# Dev (Node.js path on this machine — Cursor's bundled node)
$env:Path = "C:\Users\chara\AppData\Local\Programs\cursor\resources\app\resources\helpers;$env:LOCALAPPDATA\pnpm;$env:Path"
pnpm dev                          # http://localhost:3000

# Database (Docker Desktop must be running)
docker compose up -d postgres
pnpm exec prisma migrate deploy
pnpm db:seed                      # creates admin + 5 agents + 3 spaces + demo tasks

# Quality
pnpm lint
pnpm test                         # vitest run (62+ tests)
pnpm exec next build --webpack    # full type check + production build

# Git
git status -s
git log --oneline -10
```

**Admin login (dev):** `admin@example.com` / `ChangeMe123!`

